CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 12, 1954, pg. 4, reads: "Pitt Graduation - These young men and women were among the 1561 who were granted degrees Wednesday at the spring commencement of the University of Pittsburgh. They are, left to right:..K. Leroy Irvis, one of the top graduates in School of Law;...-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh School of Law graduate K. Leroy Irvis, posed in Cathedral of Learning
